						<summary>

						<p>East wall of the same temple, left of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīra-Pāṇḍyadēva: Year 11, Aippaśi = 1276 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is damaged and incomplete. It records a gift of a <hi rend="italic">sandhyā</hi> lamp to the god Tāntōṉṟīśvaramuḍaiyār by a certain Dēvaṉ Irājarājaṉ a Veḷḷāḻaṉ Śōḻa of Nambipērūr in Vaḍapariśāra-nāḍu. The <hi rend="italic">Śivabrāhmaṇas</hi> figuring in No. 216 above, figure here also.</p>						

						</summary>
